}}{{TIDTOC|embedded}} ==Overview== "10016298" and "V2.0" (FCC EUT) or "V2.1" <!--(some / all current production models)--> is silkscreened on the board. :Two [http://www.skyworksinc.com/Product.aspx?ProductID=964 '''Skyworks''' SE2605L] PAMs are in use :.. as well as two ICs marked w/ (at least) S318 (7446)
The power adapter shown in the FCC external photos is a :'''Shenzhen Heweishun Network Technology Co, Ltd.''' TEA09U-09100 (100-240VAC ~ 50/60Hz, 0.3A -> 9VDC, 1.0A).
==Links of Interest== *[https://forum.openwrt.org/viewtopic.php?id=49029 On the '''OpenWrt''' forums] eCos would seem to be the stock OS
